properties.Name: DeviceEventType
properties.Description:
A type of event that can be recorded for a Device.

Ex:
- Trade-in
- Installation
- Repair
- Replacement
- Loss
- Theft
- Casualty Loss
- Cannibalization
- Salvage
- Production
- Injected
- Plugged
- Abandoned
- Sale
- Transfer
